    "# Themes"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Load cuxfilter and data"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from cuxfilter import charts\n",
    "import cuxfilter\n",
    "from bokeh import palettes\n",
    "cux_df = cuxfilter.DataFrame.from_arrow('./data/146M_predictions_v2.arrow')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Declare charts"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "MAPBOX_API_KEY= \"pk.eyJ1IjoiYXRob3J2ZSIsImEiOiJjazBmcmlhYzAwYXc2M25wMnE3bGttbzczIn0.JCDQliLc-XTU52iKa8L8-Q\"\n",
    "\n",
    "chart1 = charts.choropleth(x='zip', y='delinquency_12_prediction', color_column='delinquency_12_prediction', color_aggregate_fn='mean',\n",
    "                                  geoJSONSource = 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/rapidsai/cuxfilter/GTC-2018-mortgage-visualization/javascript/demos/GTC%20demo/public/data/zip3-ms-rhs-lessprops.json',\n",
    "                                  data_points=1000, nan_color='white',\n",
    "                                  mapbox_api_key=MAPBOX_API_KEY)\n",
    "chart2 = charts.bar('borrower_credit_score')\n",
    "chart_widget = charts.multi_select('dti')\n",
    "\n",
    "#create a list of charts\n",
    "charts_list = [chart_widget, chart1, chart2]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Themes Types"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 1. Light"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "d = cux_df.dashboard(charts_list, layout=cuxfilter.layouts.feature_and_base, theme=cuxfilter.themes.light, title=\"Theme - light\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 10,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
